OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FSpectator Shane Ogden captured the
OL,7,Fmoment two jets crashed during an air
OL,8,Fshow
OL,10,FAll four crew members ejected safely
OL,11,Fafter two US military jets collided
OL,12,Fduring an air show at a military base
OL,13,Fin Idaho.
OL,15,FSocial media videos, shared by
OL,16,Fspectators, show four parachutes
OL,17,Fopening in the sky as the aircraft, US
OL,18,FNavy EA-18G Growlers, plummet to the
OL,19,Fground near the base, about 50 miles
OL,20,Fsouth of Boise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
