OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779188575
OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FVideo shot by spectator Shane Ogden
OL,7,Fshowed the moment of impact - and the
OL,8,Fcrews' incredible escape.
OL,10,FIn the video, the planes collide
OL,11,Fbefore spinning in tandem as the crew
OL,12,Fmembers eject and their parachutes
OL,13,Fopen.
OL,15,FThe planes then fall together,
OL,16,Fexploding into a fireball upon impact
OL,17,Fas the crew members drift to the
OL,18,Fground nearby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
