FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779188575
OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FIn a text message, Ogden wrote: "I was
OL,7,Fjust filming thinking they were going
OL,8,Fto split apart and that happened and I
OL,9,Ffilmed the rest."
OL,11,FOgden said he left soon after the
OL,12,Fcrash because he did not want to get
OL,13,Fin the way of emergency responders.
OL,15,FOfficials say that the four crew
OL,16,Fmembers are in stable condition and
OL,17,Fthat the remainder of the Gunfighter
OL,18,FSkies air show has been cancelled.
