OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FAmelia Umayam, spokesperson for Naval
OL,7,FAir Forces, US Pacific Fleet, says
OL,8,Fthat the navy is investigating the
OL,9,Fcrash.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe aircraft were performing an aerial
OL,17,Fdemonstration when the crash occurred.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
