PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779188575
OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FAccording to an aviation safety
OL,7,Fexpert, it was remarkable both crews
OL,8,Fwere able to eject from their planes,
OL,9,Fas they are not often able to eject
OL,10,Fduring a mid-air collision.
OL,12,FJeff Guzzetti said: "It's really
OL,13,Fstriking to see. It looks like they
OL,14,Fstruck each other in a very unique
OL,15,Ffashion to cause them to remain intact
OL,16,Fand kind of stick to each other and
OL,17,Fthat very well could have saved them."
OL,26,@tD@UOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
