PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779188575
OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FHe added: "It appears to be a pilot
OL,7,Fissue to me. It doesn't look like it
OL,8,Fwas a mechanical malfunction.
OL,9,FRendezvousing with another airplane in
OL,10,Fformation flight is challenging, and
OL,11,Fit has to be done just right to
OL,12,Fprevent exactly this kind of thing."
OL,14,FThis is the first time in eight years
OL,15,Fthat the Gunfighter Skies air show has
OL,16,Fgone ahead, and it is not the first
OL,17,Fincident.
