PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779188575
OL,3,CCrew parachute to safety after two US
OL,4,Cmilitary jets collide during air show
OL,6,FJohn Cudahy, president and CEO of the
OL,7,FInternational Council of Air Shows,
OL,8,Fsaid that there used to be an average
OL,9,Fof about two deaths a year at a US air
OL,10,Fshow. However, over the past decade,
OL,11,Fthe average has been closer to one
OL,12,Fdeath a year, and a spectator has not
OL,13,Fbeen killed at an air show in the US
OL,14,Fsince 1952.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
